&lt;/div>
&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Gunbreaker Skills Overview</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/skills-overview/</link><pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:27:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/skills-overview/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="gunbreaker-skills-overview">Gunbreaker Skills Overview&lt;/h1>
